thread.title: BRIEF-Ericsson wins cash suite order
thread.title_full: BRIEF-Ericsson wins cash suite order | Reuters

author: Reuters
title: BRIEF-Ericsson wins cash suite order
text:
Sept 22 Telefonaktiebolaget L M Ericsson
* Ericsson Order to Cash suite consisting of Charging System, Ericsson Multi Mediation and Multi Activation software will be deployed in all MTN networks.
* Ericsson will also provide Support Services and Managed Services for the suite Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: (Reporting By Johan Ahlander)
